lence），但香港年輕人可獲原諒，因為他們對香港的未來感到沮喪、無助，甚至對缺乏方向和共同願景感到憤怒，<span style=\"color: red;\">而接連的特首均未能說服他們，香港的未來會比回歸前更明亮</span>。然而葉劉認為放棄「一國兩制」是愚蠢的（fatuous），《基本法》仍是維持香港獨立制度、權利、自由，以及獨特生活方式的最佳保障，沒有「一國兩制」，香港將會在中國失去的經濟及政治影響力，確實（indeed）成為另一個中國城市。<br />\n<br />\n文章提到，「一國兩制」是政治妥協，需要互相理解和克制才能維持所需微妙平衡，<span style=\"color: red;\">特首有責任說服中國甚麼對香港最好，並通過展現有效和全面解釋《基本法》可解決香港餘下的衝突，爭取大眾的支持</span>。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.post852.com/280465/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.post852.com%2F280465%2F&d=ng3vG9SJ7BvQZwuOeCzNpbTKTGNgLIIXgyzGYx6bzTs%3D&h=17d1fdaf\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.post852.com/280465/</a></blockquote><br />\n全部其實都係意指林奠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4209bbad2ab351377f435a3ef687f25d83a09a8","tid":1296961,"uid":188310,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T14:03:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EFa4phu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEFa4phu.jpg&h=53ca421b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"42b167a3bce0c44021a07996ce7c253601ef7172","tid":1296961,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a46aad7925ed71f7277e7d5c8d35587bdc8305d3","tid":1296961,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T13:49:58.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">特首有責任說服中國甚麼對香港最好</span><br />\n呢個時勢仲想叫特首硬銷中國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T14:06:12.000Z","msg":"佢似硬銷自己lor😒"},{"pid":"adf53f69a84ba692a9129d8b7546740f051c8d8c","tid":1296961,"uid":39777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T14:08:02.000Z","msg":"香港年輕人可獲原諒，因為他們對香港的未來感到沮喪、無助，甚至對缺乏方向和共同願景感到憤怒，而接連的特首均未能說服他們，香港的未來會比回歸前更明亮。<br />\n<br />\n其實講得都無錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/so